HEADWORD: M-1
<hw>M-1</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A semiautomatic rifle which was standard
issue to infantrymen in the United States Army in the mid-20th
century.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Garand rifle, Garand, M-1 rifle.</syn>⟦br⟧
